title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 10 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 10 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 3: Clay and Buck welcome Sen. Rand Paul to talk government's contradictory covid response. YouTube has banned Sen. Paul for seven days. How to resist the left's covid power grab. You are more likely to die from seasonal flu or struck by lightning than die of covid. With the help of 19 GOP senators, out-of-control infrastructure bill passes. Will Cuomo run for New York governor again? Judge wants to force January 6th protesters to pay for monthslong National Guard.
